that little scooter.

101
00:06:05,618 --> 00:06:09,418
Oh, don't give me that look.

102
00:06:09,522 --> 00:06:11,956
I happen to be
a more caring mother than most.

103
00:06:12,057 --> 00:06:15,083
- Where's my bed?
