- Hmm.

111
00:06:40,853 --> 00:06:44,482
<i>Lucille decided she needed
the help of Buster's father.</i>

112
00:06:44,590 --> 00:06:47,354
<i>Unfortunately,
after a recent escape attempt...</i>

113
00:06:47,459 --> 00:06:50,587
