put in solitary confinement.</i>

114
00:07:17,857 --> 00:07:20,417
<i>Michael went to find
his brother at his latest gig.</i>

115
00:07:20,526 --> 00:07:22,858
- What's up, Mike?
- Yeah. What are you doing here?

116
00:07:22,962 --> 00:07:25,760
